"Venus in Furs (German: Venus im Pelz) is a novella by the Austrian author Leopold von Sacher-Masoch, and the best known of his works. The novel was to be part of an epic series that Sacher-Masoch envisioned called Legacy of Cain (Das Verm\u00e4chtni\u00df Kains). Venus in Furs was part of Love (Die Liebe), the first volume of the series. It was published in 1870.\n\n"